data.title: Tower of Power: 50th Anniversary Tour
data.meta_description: Get the latest information regarding Camden County events. Be sure to check back often for the latest news and notes regarding activities in Camden County.
data.text:
Presented by the Camden County Board of Freeholders in association with BRE and the Borough of Collingswood, the Scottish Rite Auditorium welcomes the Tower of Power: 50th Anniversary Tour with special guests Average White Band! Doors open at 7 PM, showtime at 8 PM. Tower of Power is an American R&B-based horn section and band that has been performing since 1968. Tower of Power has been delivering their unique brand of soul music to their fans and “Souled Out”…
